<br>
would uber guilds add them to the list of mobs who's reservations need to be deleted?(like VS?)<br>
<br>
<br>
What would be nice is to see some 55th and 57th level caps put on mobs that are in competition, and &quot;easy&quot; for the uber highlevel set.  Of course their loot would be moved to other monsters that would provide a challenge for the 57+ set of players.  That would definately solve some problems i think, of course im sure you could add them to the loot table in such a way it wouldnt make epics more easily attainable, if that were a concern at this time.<br>
<br>
